## Task Details

### T-001: Database Schema
**Priority:** high
**Problem:** No data model defined.
**Solution:** Design Prisma schema with entities, relations, and indexes.
**Files:** `prisma/schema.prisma`
**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] All entities with relationships defined
- [ ] Indexes on frequently queried fields
- [ ] Migration runs cleanly

### T-002: Core CRUD Endpoints
**Priority:** high
**Problem:** No API endpoints.
**Solution:** Build REST routes with service layer.
**Files:** `src/routes/`, `src/services/`
**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] GET (list + detail), POST, PUT, DELETE for each entity
- [ ] Proper HTTP status codes (200, 201, 400, 404, 500)
- [ ] Transactions for related mutations

### T-003: Auth Middleware
**Priority:** high
**Problem:** No authentication.
**Solution:** {{ auth_strategy | upper }} auth middleware.
**Files:** `src/middleware/auth.ts`, `src/routes/auth.ts`
**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] Login/register endpoints (if JWT)
- [ ] Protected route middleware
- [ ] Token validation

### T-004: Input Validation
**Priority:** high
**Problem:** No request validation.
**Solution:** Zod schemas for all request bodies.
**Files:** `src/models/`, `src/middleware/validate.ts`
**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] Zod schema per endpoint
- [ ] Validation middleware rejects invalid input
- [ ] Descriptive error messages

### T-005: Error Handling
**Priority:** medium
**Problem:** No structured error responses.
**Solution:** Global error handler middleware.
**Files:** `src/middleware/error.ts`
**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] All errors returned as JSON
- [ ] No internal details leaked in production
- [ ] Proper status codes for different error types

